{
  "stem": "7722.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He could-- he was so good, he-- he could give you an estimate 10% more or 10% less.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And besides this, he was-- when they chopped the trees, they made different kind of things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The most of them, they made from oak trees they made-- they called this, I don't know in English, the English term, they called this [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They made, with them-- for the barrels to age the scotch, scotch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they made different kind-- different kind of things for buildings and other things they made.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was the one who-- who watched they should do the right-- the right thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And did the same thing, and he paid the-- the workers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was his job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before-- before the second-- before the First World War, he used to come home only twice a year for Passover holidays and for-- and for this, I guess, Rosh Hashanah, and I mean, New Year's and-- and sukkot [BACKGROUND NOISE] he used to stay-- I don't-- I was a child.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Used to stay three weeks, or four weeks or five weeks, and he went-- and he went back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on, when we moved during the-- the First World War, when we moved to Mizocz, so we were a family together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, where?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was over there-- very, very active.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Not really a cantor, just he use-- I don't know if you know what it means, the meaning [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are-- when you-- when you're [NON-ENGLISH] or [NON-ENGLISH], you have two parts, the first and the second.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father used to blow the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father used  to daven over there, [NON-ENGLISH] always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not-- not [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was a-- a religious man.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
